message: "If you use Joanium in your work or research, please cite it using this metadata."
type: software
title: "Joanium"
abstract: >
  Joanium is a local-first AI desktop assistant that combines multi-model chat,
  scheduled automations, background agents, MCP server support, and native
  integrations with GitHub, Gmail, Google Drive, and more — without sending
  data to the cloud.
